snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance - Of Minds, Blades and Schnapps! [NA]
snippet.description:
Take a closer look at our gameplay features in Kingdom Come: Deliverance and follow Henry on an exciting day through medieval Bohemia!

Kingdom Come: Deliverance will be available worldwide on February 13th 2018! Pre-order Now: http://kcd.kochmedia.com
